                </div>
                <h3 class="ml-2 font-medium text-gray-900">Essential Cookies</h3>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Required for the operation of our website, including login areas and shopping carts</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-100">
              <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
                <div class="bg-indigo-100 rounded-full p-1">
                  <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-600" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="ml-2 font-medium text-gray-900">Analytical/Performance</h3>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Help us recognize and count visitors and analyze how they use our website</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-100">
              <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
                <div class="bg-indigo-100 rounded-full p-1">
                  <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-600" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z" />
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="ml-2 font-medium text-gray-900">Functionality Cookies</h3>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Recognize you when you return and personalize your experience</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-100">
              <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
                <div class="bg-indigo-100 rounded-full p-1">
                  <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-indigo-600" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 3.055A9.001 9.001 0 1020.945 13H11V3.055z" />
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M20.488 9H15V3.512A9.025 9.025 0 0120.488 9z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="ml-2 font-medium text-gray-900">Targeting Cookies</h3>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Record your visit, pages visited, and links followed to make our advertising more relevant</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <%# Types of Cookies Card %>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm overflow-hidden mb-8">
        <div class="p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 bg-indigo-600 rounded-md p-2">
              <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-white" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 21a4 4 0 01-4-4V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v12a4 4 0 01-4 4zm0 0h12a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2.343M11 7.343l1.657-1.657a2 2 0 012.828 0l2.829 2.829a2 2 0 010 2.828l-8.486 8.485M7 17h.01" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2 class="ml-4 text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Types of Cookies We Use</h2>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-6 mt-4">
            <div class="bg-indigo-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-indigo-900 mb-2">Session Cookies</h3>
              <p class="text-indigo-700">
                Session cookies are temporary cookies that are used to remember you during the course of your visit to the website, and they expire when you close the web browser.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-indigo-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-indigo-900 mb-2">Persistent Cookies</h3>
              <p class="text-indigo-700">
                Persistent cookies are used to remember your preferences within the website and remain on your desktop or mobile device even after you close your browser or restart your computer.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-indigo-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-indigo-900 mb-2">Third-Party Cookies</h3>
              <p class="text-indigo-700">
                We also use various third-party cookies to report usage statistics of the website and deliver advertisements on and through the website.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <%# Cookie Management Card %>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm overflow-hidden mb-8">
        <div class="p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 bg-indigo-600 rounded-md p-2">
              <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-white" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z" />
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2 class="ml-4 text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Cookie Management</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
